        public SubmitDocumentResponse submitNewDocument(SubmitDocumentRequest submitDocumentRequest)
                                         throws DocumentException
        Submits new document. USername and token are extracted from the request and the external system's SecurityService is called. If the provided authentication has passed the document can continue processing. If not, throw exception and return error code.
